name: sawdust, wet, measured as dry mass to generic market for residual softwood, wet | residual softwood, wet | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/22426/documentation

This activity is linking the more specific market for saw dust, to the more generic market for residual softwood, wet; and residual hardwood, wet.It makes accesible the specific product saw dust through the more generic products of wet residual wood.;[This dataset is meant to replace the following datasets:; - saw dust, wet, measured as dry mass to generic market for residual softwood, wet, RER, 2014 - 2014 (beaa32b1-19ff-4ea9-aa1c-6db9bafcab10)];[This dataset is meant to replace the following datasets:; - saw dust, wet, measured as dry mass to generic market for residual softwood, wet, RER, 2014 - 2014 (beaa32b1-19ff-4ea9-aa1c-6db9bafcab10)]

Entry of the specific product "saw dust, wet, measured as dry mass"

Delivery of the generic products "residual softwood, wet" and "residual hardwood, wet"
